category: Perl
requires: perl perl-Pod-Escapes
sdesc: "Perl POD parser module"
ldesc: "Pod-Simple is a Perl library for parsing text in the Pod
('plain old documentation') markup language that is typically used for
writing documentation for Perl and for Perl modules. The Pod format is
explained in the perlpod man page; the most common formatter is called
'perldoc'."
